OL,5, A dad left without medication for two  
OL,6, weeks due to supply issues says the rug
OL,7, has been pulled from under him.        
OL,9,FSimon Hawkins, from Caerphilly, said it
OL,10,Fwas unnerving not to have his attention
OL,11,Fdeficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)  
OL,12,Ftablets.                               
OL,14,FIt comes as prescribers are told not to
OL,15,Foffer certain ADHD medications to new  
OL,16,Fpatients while high demand and         
OL,17,Fmanufacturing issues are resolved.     
OL,19,FThe Welsh government said other        
OL,20,Ftreatments were available.             
